      "content": "i was just looking at some photos of deep space cosmics or whatever and it just hit me... like, in a billion years everything is just gonna be gone. every single thing we ever did, every person that ever lived, it's all just a temporary glitch in a vacuum that doesn't even care. it feels so pointless to even try anymore. why bother with anything if the end result is just nothingness?"
